一、[servlet]-servlet.xml

    <mvc:annotation-driven/>
         <mvc:resources location="/imgs/" mapping="/imgs/**"/>
   
二、web.xml

<servlet-mapping>
     <servlet-name>default</servlet-name>
     <url-pattern>*.jpg</url-pattern>
 </servlet-mapping>

三、base标签

<base href="${pagecontext.request.getcontextpath }/170207/">

一和二为过滤，三为路径匹配
